com.pi4j.system

Interface SystemInfoProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BananaPiSystemInfoProvider, BananaProSystemInfoProvider, DefaultSystemInfoProvider, OdroidSystemInfoProvider, RaspiSystemInfoProvider, SystemInfoProviderBase

    public interface SystemInfoProvider
    SystemInfo provider interface. Used to support multiple platforms where each may need to have a platform specific implementation of the system info.
